{"tid":1708393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足們 11點好返屋企啦！","createTime":"2019-11-11T14:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:16:03.000Z","uid":212819,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbacb6f6d64db6ec1851aad8dd7a61528621ea3","tid":1708393,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"有手足講過11點係班狗換更既時候<br />\n所以11點後既狗特別精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以手足依家留返馬路上既垃圾等班狗狗清理<br />\n清到聽朝就差唔多無哂精力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而手足們11點依個時候就應該返屋企訓教 養精蓄銳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訓夠先可以早起身 快閃都跑快兩步<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以手足們 聽日黎明既時候再見！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb7a0ae834a315f4f3fea79ffc41839e1de3fe8","tid":1708393,"uid":173137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddbacb6f6d64db6ec1851aad8dd7a61528621ea3","tid":1708393,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"有手足講過11點係班狗換更既時候<br />\n所以11點後既狗特別精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以手足依家留返馬路上既垃圾等班狗狗清理<br />\n清到聽朝就差唔多無哂精力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而手足們11點依個時候就應該返屋企訓教 養精蓄銳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訓夠先可以早起身 快閃都跑快兩步<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以手足們 聽日黎明既時候再見！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"走啊！"},{"pid":"3f04582ff5a2b0e085f46f5ffbdaeb814a54c553","tid":1708393,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pi